{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_01_04",
  "title": "サニーピース 01 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ新人オーディション、面接当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the Hoshimi Prods new idol audition interviews.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルになると決めた私は、お姉ちゃんと一緒に）\n（芸能事務所のオーディションを受けることにした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Having decided to become an idol‚ I)\n(decided to take the audition for a talent agency)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.8458730221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "（憧れのアイドル、長瀬麻奈ちゃんが所属していた）\n（星見プロのオーディションを……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(with my sister.)\n(The Hoshimi Pro audition…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "うう……ここにいるのって\nみんなオーディションを受ける子だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… everyone here…\nare they all here for the audition?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い子ばっかり……私、場違いじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're all so cute… I don't belong here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗も書類選考を突破してここにいるんだから\nもっと自信を持ちなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ you passed the document screening and you're here‚\nso be more confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "でもいきなり面接なんて……\n人と話すの、苦手なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But suddenly having an interview…\nI'm not good at talking to people…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "弱気にならないで、胸を張って堂々としなさい\n私と一緒にアイドルになるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't be so timid‚ stand tall and be confident.\nWe're going to be idols together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……そうだね\nお姉ちゃんとアイドルになるために、頑張る！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes… you're right.\nI'll do my best to become an idol with Saki-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "その意気よ。必ず二人でアイドルになりましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's the spirit. Let's definitely become idols together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、次の方どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next‚ please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333293599999,
