        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4016.666666699997,
          "startTime": 65.75
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "は、はいっ！　失礼します！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes! Excuse me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "では自己紹介をお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ please introduce yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "し、白石千紗、高校二年生です……\nよろしくお願いします……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Chisa Shiraishi… s-second-year high school student…\nPleased to meet you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "白石……？\nああ、さっき面接した白石沙季さんの妹さんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shiraishi…?\nAh‚ you're the younger sister of Saki Shiraishi‚ who I just interviewed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばお姉さんとの面接で\nあなたの話題が出ましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ you came up\nduring our conversation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　お姉ちゃんが私の話を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Saki-chan talked about me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "妹がいてくれたから、アイドルになろうと\n思うようになった……そう言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said that because she has a younger sister‚\nshe decided to become an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがそんなことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan said that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんとは仲がいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you close to your sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "は、はいっ！　とっても仲良しなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes! We're very close!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの……お姉ちゃんは凄いんです！\n美人で頭も良くて生徒会長をするくらい人気があって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… my sister is amazing!\nShe's beautiful‚ smart‚ and popular enough to be",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "しっかり者で整理整頓が得意で\n厳しい時もあるけど本当はとっても優しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the student council president. She's reliable‚ good at organizing‚\nand although she can be strict‚ she's actually very kind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "計画的に進めるタイプで、アイドルになるって\n決めてからは歌とダンスのレッスンも始めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's a planner‚ and after deciding to become an idol‚\nshe started taking singing and dancing lessons…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8273197114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
