      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 280.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "やったわ千紗！　私、オーディション合格だって！\nこれでアイドルになれるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did it‚ Chisa! I passed the audition!\nI can be an idol now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 287.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう、お姉ちゃん……\nやっぱりお姉ちゃんは凄いなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations‚ Saki-chan…\nYou're amazing‚ Saki-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 292.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗？　もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa? Don't tell me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 294.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "うん、不合格だった……でも当然だよね\n私より可愛い子ばっかりだったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I failed… but it's only natural.\nThere were so many girls who were prettier than me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 303.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "面接では何も面白いことが言えなくて……\n実技審査もうまく踊れなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't say anything interesting during the interview…\nAnd I couldn't dance well during the practical exam…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "こんな私じゃ、選ばれなくても仕方ないよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's no wonder I wasn't chosen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 315.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、そんなに落ち込まないで\nオーディションに一度落ちただけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ don't be so down.\nYou just failed one audition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 320.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションなら他にも沢山あるんだから\n諦めないでまた受けてみたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are plenty of other auditions out there‚\nso don't give up and try again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 326.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだよ……。だって、私の夢は\nお姉ちゃんと一緒にアイドルになることなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's no use… Because my dream\nis to be an idol with you‚ Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 334.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと一緒じゃなきゃ\nオーディションを受ける意味ないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's not with Saki-chan‚\nthere's no point in auditioning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 339.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "だったら私も合格を辞退するわ。それでまた一緒に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll decline my acceptance. And we'll take it together again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 345.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "それは絶対ダメ！\n私はお姉ちゃんに迷惑を掛けたくないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can't do that!\nI don't want to be a burden to you‚ Saki-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 350.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs034.m4a",
      "text": "もういいの……お姉ちゃんとオーディションを受けて\nちょっとの間だけでも夢を見られて、満足したから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay… I'm satisfied with having seen a glimpse of my dream‚\neven if it was only for a short time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 355.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 366.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_01_04-chs035.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もう出来もしない夢を追いかけるのは諦める\n……私は、アイドルになるのを諦めるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I'm giving up on chasing a dream that I can't achieve.\n…I'm giving up on being an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 366.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
